## SEO Enhancements
- **Per-page metadata** with unique title, description, OG tags on every route
- **JSON-LD** structured data (`LocalBusiness`) in root layout
- **Dynamic sitemap** at `/sitemap.xml` with all 17 routes + priorities
- **robots.txt** allowing all bots, blocking `/api/`
- **Trailing slashes** matching WordPress URLs exactly
- **Server Components** by default for fast TTFB

## CRO & Lead Capture
- **Exit-intent popup** on desktop (fires once per session)
- **Sticky mobile CTA bar** on mobile (Call Now + Book a Space)
- **Lead form** on every service page sidebar + contact page
- **WhatsApp floating button** on every page
- **API route** at `/api/contact/` — supports Google Sheets + email (env vars)

